document_data.name: Dust Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Dust Alley''' was a small backalley that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Waterdeep}}
document_data.Location: Dust Alley was located in Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]]. The alley branched off of the east side of [[Three Daggers Alley]] at two point. It extended north to connect with [[Blackstar Lane]].
